# Claude Code local state
# Match platxa-code-agent convention: ignore everything in .claude/ except
# explicitly re-included paths below. Spec workflow state, research history,
# findings, snapshots, and progress logs are local-only — not committed.
.claude/*
.claude-plugin/.claude/
**/.claude/shared_state.json
# Re-include shareable sub-paths once they exist:
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/output-styles/
!.claude/init.sh
!.claude/CHANGELOG.md
CLAUDE.local.md

